Duke version 1.0.0

	Duke is an opensource high resolution video player dedicated to
	visual effect and post production companies.
	

License

	see COPYING file


Compilation

	* Getting the source
		git clone git://github.com/mikrosimage/duke.git
		cd duke
		git submodule update -i

	* External libraries
		A few external libraries are mandatory to build duke.
		Please customize 'site-config.jam.example' and move it to (BOOST_ROOT)/tools/build/v2/site-config.jam
		When you're done, don't forget to uncomment the file's last line.

	* Compilation
		see INSTALL file


Tested compilers

	* Linux
		+ GCC 4.4.1 on OpenSUSE 11.2
	* MacOS
		+ GCC 4.2.1 on OSX 10.5 Leopard
	* Windows
		+ gcc (tdm-1) 4.5.2 on Windows XP ( http://tdm-gcc.tdragon.net/ )


